<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="C客戶">
  <data key="d0">C客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">客戶</data>
  <data key="d2">C客戶 refers to a customer involved in a maintenance record and is integral to the documentation of these records. This entity denotes the name of the client for whom the maintenance documentation is being created and maintained. The term C客戶 specifically identifies the customer whose information is recorded within the context of a particular maintenance activity or process. Accurately identifying and documenting this customer's details in relation to any maintenance operations performed is essential.

C客戶 represents a client named "C" for whom maintenance activities were recorded by the service provider. This entity signifies that the maintenance record involves specific actions taken on behalf of the customer, ensuring that all interactions and activities are meticulously documented for future reference and accountability. The descriptions emphasize the importance of maintaining precise records to support the efficient management of services provided to C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶是一筆維護紀錄中的服務對象。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
