<node id="維護紀錄">
  <data key="d0">維護紀錄</data>
  <data key="d1">維護紀錄</data>
  <data key="d2">Maintenance records, such as 維護紀錄, provide comprehensive documentation of maintenance activities performed for various clients. These records detail the actions taken by engineers and personnel on specific dates and times, including descriptions of system statuses and issues addressed.

For example, one record pertains to Customer C and documents the actions taken by Engineer B from 13:30 to 17:30 on October 13, 2025. Another entry involves work carried out by personnel for a different client, including detailed information about authorized usage, server performance, version update recommendations, and activities conducted between 9:00 AM and 5:00 PM on December 24, 2025.

There is also a record for Customer E that details the maintenance work performed from November 12 to December 23, 2025. For instance, actions were taken from 13:30 to 17:40 on November 12, 2025, addressing issues with full disk space and data synchronization for B客戶. A subsequent entry involves maintenance tasks performed by Person A and Person C, including detailed handling times and status descriptions.

Additionally, the record captures specific instances like a document detailing actions taken between 9:30 AM to 4:30 PM on October 20, 2025, by B personnel for Customer C. This includes handling times and status descriptions of system statuses and issues addressed. Another entry records the work performed from 11:00 to 16:00 on December 23, 2025, by C personnel for E客户.

In summary, 維護紀錄 encompasses detailed logs that capture a comprehensive account of maintenance tasks across different clients and personnel involved. The records include handling times, status descriptions, and the actions taken to address issues such as server performance, system optimization suggestions, and version updates.&lt;SEP&gt;這是一筆關於C客戶的維護紀錄，記錄了從2025/03/14 09:00至2025/03/14 14:00的處理過程和結果。&lt;SEP&gt;Maintenance record of activities performed by Engineer B for C客戶on 2025/11/11 between 13:30 and 17:30.&lt;SEP&gt;這是一份關於C客戶的維護紀錄，包含了處理時間、狀態描述和處置動作等信息。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7743e93210e95e8e40e0d2a627684b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1df6d8d113790f99d50593095e1e5e58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5618eb566fb322ada0eb69bef88a7581&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-345e520afd2a192e25824abb33740d46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b</data>
