  <data key="d1">狀態描述</data>
  <data key="d2">The entity FISAC資料收容-進行中 refers to an ongoing task involving data intake and containment for FISAC, which is carried out through the submission of API IP application forms. This project is currently in progress, with相关部门正在处理FISAC资料收集的工作。B部门已经请james向FISAC提交了需要使用API的IP申请单，以完成这一任务。目前已提交了API IP申请单至FISAC，整个过程仍在进行中。

The process involves B department handling the data collection for FISAC, with James being responsible for submitting the required API IP application forms. It is clear that multiple steps are involved in this ongoing action, from preparing and submitting the necessary applications to managing the actual data intake and containment operations.</data>
