<node id="World Athletics Federation">
  <data key="d0">World Athletics Federation</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The World Athletics Federation oversees global track and field competitions, including the organization and regulation of events like the World Athletics Championships. It is responsible for validating world records across various disciplines such as the 100m sprint record set by athletes like Noah Carter. The federation plays a key role in ensuring consistency and integrity in athletics records, whether these are set during major international competitions or other global track and field events. Its oversight encompasses not only organizing high-profile championships but also verifying performances to maintain credible standards within the sport of athletics.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees global track and field competitions including the validation of records like the 100m sprint.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees global athletics competitions like the World Athletics Championship and is responsible for validating records such as Noah Carter's 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees global athletics competitions like the World Athletics Championship and validates new records.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56b76e765b58a558604d5d6f2575d2ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7743e93210e95e8e40e0d2a627684b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dddcb833d814b293bd936732652206d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b</data>
