  <data key="d2">Alarm Inventory (告警盤點) is a pending item listed for completion in maintenance work. It is one of the tasks that needs to be carried out and involves conducting an inventory of alarms. The task is categorized as part of the pending work items requiring further action. Scheduled to start next week, this task aims to systematically review and manage alarm notifications, ensuring all alerts are accounted for and addressed appropriately.</data>
