<edge source="C客戶" target="維護紀錄">
  <data key="d7">8.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (C客戶, 維護紀錄) pertains to a maintenance record that details services rendered to customer C. This maintenance record involves documenting actions and issues for C客戶and covers work items and status descriptions related to the client. The document provides an account of the relevant maintenance activities conducted for C客户 within specific time periods by B人员, detailing the service provided and any associated issues or tasks involved in maintaining the customer's needs.</data>
  <data key="d9">client service,customer record,customer service,maintenance log,maintenance record,maintenance service,record,service recipient,服務對象,維護,維護活動,記錄</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773694418</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="C客戶" target="B人員">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">B人員被指派为处理C客户的维护工作。&lt;SEP&gt;B人員負責為C客戶進行維護工作。&lt;SEP&gt;B人員作為工程師正在為C客戶的維護紀錄進行相關的工作。&lt;SEP&gt;B人員負責處理C客戶的維護工作，包括一系列處置動作。</data>
  <data key="d9">工程師指派,工程師處理,工程師責任,維護,維護工作,維護工程,處置動作</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e</data>
