<edge source="B人員" target="維護紀錄">
  <data key="d7">10.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between (B人员, 维护纪录) involves Engineer B personnel being responsible for handling and documenting various maintenance tasks. Engineer B is assigned the responsibility of performing the tasks listed in this maintenance record specifically for Customer C. This includes not only executing the documented activities but also creating and updating the maintenance records to reflect any changes or adjustments made during the process.

B人员 is tasked with managing all aspects of the maintenance work, which encompasses updating and adjusting as needed. They are directly involved in performing the maintenance activities recorded within these documents for C客户. The tasks performed by Engineer B personnel include both executing the maintenance actions and documenting them to ensure a complete record of all performed activities. This comprehensive approach ensures that the maintenance record is accurate and up-to-date, providing a detailed account of the work done on behalf of Customer C.&lt;SEP&gt;Engineer B performed the activities documented in the maintenance record for Client C.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員負責處理C客戶的維護工作，記錄在維護紀錄中。</data>
  <data key="d9">engineer activity,engineer assignment,engineer handling,engineer involvement,engineer responsibility,engineering work,handling,maintenance,maintenance action,maintenance activity,maintenance documentation,service provider,task execution,執行工程師,工程師工作,工程師維護,維護,維護活動,處理工作</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b</data>
