<edge source="維護紀錄" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">20.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (C personnel, maintenance record) involves C personnel as engineers responsible for various maintenance activities documented within a specific maintenance record. As processing engineers, C personnel are engaged in all maintenance activities recorded in the maintenance record and handle maintenance work for different clients such as H客户, E客户, B客户, and I客户. They ensure that all tasks and technical issues related to these clients are addressed and properly documented.

C personnel play a crucial role by not only participating in handling the tasks detailed in the maintenance records but also taking corresponding actions to address any technical problems encountered during the process. This includes maintaining a comprehensive record of their activities for each client they serve, ensuring meticulous documentation and effective management of all aspects of maintenance work. For instance, C personnel have conducted maintenance for E客户 and B客户, updating the relevant information in the same maintenance record.

The maintenance record documents the actions taken by these engineers to resolve any issues that arise during the maintenance process. Therefore, C personnel are integral to ensuring that all activities and problems encountered during maintenance operations are comprehensively recorded and managed efficiently.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員也參與了此維護紀錄中的維修工作。&lt;SEP&gt;工程師C人員處理了此維護紀錄中的工作事項。&lt;SEP&gt;工程師C人員參與了此次維護操作。&lt;SEP&gt;C人員負責處理該維護紀錄。&lt;SEP&gt;C人員參與了此次對C客戶的維護工作，並記錄於維護紀錄中。</data>
  <data key="d9">document updates,engineer activity,engineer handling,engineer involvement,engineer maintenance,engineer responsible,engineer_maintenance,engineering action,engineering work,handled_by,handling engineer,handling record,maintenance action,maintenance engineer,maintenance execution,maintenance work,maintenance_engineer,problem resolution,record,record update,service execution,work,work record,工程師工作,工程師活動,工程師處理,工程師責任,維護工作,維護行動,處理,處理維護</data>
