<edge source="維護紀錄" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">11.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (B客戶, 維護紀錄) refers to a maintenance record created for B客戶. This maintenance record documents various activities and services provided for the client. The document covers multiple aspects of system maintenance performed on B客戶’s systems. Specifically, it includes details about the issues faced by B客戶 and the solutions implemented to address these problems. Additionally, there is a specific entry in this maintenance record detailing the activities conducted on November 12, 2025. Overall, the (B客戶, 維護紀錄) relation comprehensively records all relevant maintenance work and problem-solving actions undertaken for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B客戶的維護紀錄詳細記錄了工程師對其系統的維護和問題處理。&lt;SEP&gt;B客戶的需求記錄在該維護紀錄中，涵蓋了多項處置動作和代辦事項。&lt;SEP&gt;維護紀錄記錄了對B客戶的維護活動和信息。</data>
  <data key="d9">client service,customer record,customer service,issue tracking,maintained,maintainer,maintenance,maintenance log,maintenance record,record,recordkeeping,客戶需求,服務提供,維護,維護對象,維護服務,記錄</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6</data>
