<edge source="維護紀錄" target="A人員">
  <data key="d7">13.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (A人員, 維護紀錄) refers to the involvement of Engineer A personnel in the maintenance activities documented within a specific maintenance record. A人員 is one of the engineers responsible for handling the tasks detailed in the maintenance record, which includes documenting the status and actions taken during the maintenance activities. Specifically, A personnel has been involved in the maintenance work described for client B客戶 as well as I客戶, where they have handled all aspects of the maintenance activities recorded. This involvement indicates that A personnel takes responsibility for parts or the entirety of the maintenance tasks as documented in these records.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員參與了B客戶的維護工作，記錄在該維護紀錄中。&lt;SEP&gt;A人員參與了I客戶的維護作業，並更新相關維護紀錄。&lt;SEP&gt;A人員是這筆維護紀錄的負責工程師之一。&lt;SEP&gt;A人員是這次維護紀錄中的處理工程師。&lt;SEP&gt;A人員參與了此維護紀錄中的維修工作。</data>
  <data key="d9">engineer activity,engineer involvement,engineer maintenance,engineering work,handling engineer,maintenance action,maintenance engineer,maintenance work,record update,responsible,service execution,work,work record,工程師,工程師執行維護,工程師活動,工程師責任,擔任維修工作,維護工作,維護活動,處理,處理工程師</data>
