<edge source="World Athletics Federation" target="100m Sprint Record">
  <data key="d7">8.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The World Athletics Federation is responsible for validating and overseeing athletic records, particularly the 100m sprint record set by Noah Carter. This validation process is crucial for the official recognition of new records in major championships. The organization ensures that any new 100m sprint record, such as the one set by Noah Carter, meets all necessary criteria before it can be officially acknowledged and included in its records. Therefore, Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record at the championship required validation from the World Athletics Federation to be officially recognized and recorded. The federation plays a pivotal role in maintaining the integrity of world athletics records, ensuring that achievements such as those by Noah Carter are accurately validated and celebrated within the athletic community.</data>
  <data key="d9">athletic achievement,athletic governance,official recognition,oversight,record validation,sports governance</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-56b76e765b58a558604d5d6f2575d2ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7743e93210e95e8e40e0d2a627684b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dddcb833d814b293bd936732652206d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773694846</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="World Athletics Federation" target="World Athletics Championship">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The World Athletics Federation organizes the World Athletics Championship and is responsible for validating records achieved during the event.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is responsible for overseeing the World Athletics Championship and validating records like those set at the event.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation organizes the World Athletics Championship and oversees the validation of new records set during the event.</data>
